name: Mobile Solution
description:
Designed to suit your needs and compliment your style, the Deluxe Backpack is filled with functionality without compromising an ounce of fashion.
Nylon fabric with vinyl trim
Interior Padded Tech Panel: fits most laptops up to 15.6" (vertically) and tablets up to 9.7"
Organization: exterior front pocket is designed with two slip pockets and a pen sleeve to organize essentials needed quickly; two interior zippered pockets provide secure accessory organization
Exterior Side Pockets: perfect for smaller personal items or water bottle; right pocket includes a Key Leash to secure and locate keys stress-free
SmartSleeve™: fits over most upright luggage handles for easy mobility

name: Tectonic Nutech
description:
The Samsonite NuTech 17” Backpack is the next generation of our best-selling Tectonic 17” Backpack. We held to the idea if it’s not broke, don’t break it and only gave the overall look an update. All of the great features, benefits, and capacity that made this style a customer favorite have not changed!

Rugged & Durable 1680D ballistic polyester fabric with water-repellant coating & signature red accents
Updated Custom Hardware
7 Exterior Pockets/Compartments for Storage: a place for everything!
2 Side Pockets: perfect to store a water bottle, umbrella, or other need-it-quick items
Dedicated, Padded Tech Compartment
Sized to fit laptops up to 17"
Sized to fit tablets up to 11”
Laptop Hammock Suspension System: Interior webbing pieces built into the bottom of the bag, provide enhanced drop protection for your laptop
Front Pocket with Organization Zip & Slip storage pockets
3 Pen Sleeves
3 Card Slots
Key Leash
Tricot lined Top Pocket: spacious enough to fit most headphones, sunglasses or other valuables needing an added layer of protection
Main compartment features ample packing space & a collapsible document sleeve to store files, notebooks, or paperwork or compress for more packing space
SmartSleeve™: fits over most upright luggage handles for hassle-free combination travel
Padded Airmesh Back Panel: breathable mesh and foam padding offer added comfort
Adjustable, padded, and contoured shoulder straps with webbing loops to use as additional attachment points

description:

name: SXK Toiletry Kit
description:
Constructed of durable 1680D Nylon fabric, the Samsonite Pro Toiletry Kit, featuring a zip bottom compartment is designed to fit all of the essentials equally balancing style and utility.
Top compartment is spacious enough to fit larger toiletries and includes 2 zippered storage pockets
Double zip bottom compartment features a wipe clean lining and elastic loops to secure everything in place during travel
Props not included with Toiletry Kit

name: SXK Slim
description:
A sleek and versatile backpack made from fabric reinforced with Dupont Kevlar fibers provides long lasting strength and durability. The Slim Backpack is loaded with interior organizational pockets and dedicated compartments for both a laptop and tablet. A quick access back lumbar pocket with the RFID Data Vault safeguards your travel essentials from identity theft. Commute in comfort with air channel mesh padding on the back and shoulder straps and an EVA padded nylon webbing top carry handle.
Fabric reinforced with Dupont Kevlar fibers for long-lasting strength and durability
Built-in USB port, provides easy connection to USB accessories for convenient, on-the-go charging (USB accessories not included)
Wireless Charging Pocket, designed to fit your wireless battery and phone for effortless charging on the go
Quick access back pocket with RFID data vault safeguards your travel essentials from identity theft
SmartSleeve feature fits over most upright handles for hassle free combination travel.
